description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 63, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Stringalong for East, 5 for South, and Stringalong for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [63 Votes, Common]
